        "action": "Increase funding for better security in the Prison Service",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Target increased funding at the Prison Service in order to improve security in and around prisons as well as avoid administrative errors including, but not limited to, accidental prisoner releases which have increased by around 120% in the past few years, as well as relieve overcrowded prisons.",
